    "Also, the goal of VAE is to maximize the lower bound of data log-likelihood.The best feature of VAE is to learn both a generative model and an inference.",
    "Although both VAE and GANs are extremely interesting methods for applying unsupervised learning to understand the underlying data distribution, GANs produce superior outcomes versus VAE.",
